            <title>[SOLR-1543] StreamingUpdateSolrServer threading bug</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1543</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;StreamingUpdateSolrServer - indexing process stops in a couple of hours&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/352d3c8cd3bbc8cb&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/352d3c8cd3bbc8cb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
